  "subject": "Docs: Replace blockdiag/seqdiag with Mermaid",
  "commit_message": "Docs: Replace blockdiag/seqdiag with Mermaid\n\nReplace the abandoned sphinxcontrib-blockdiag and sphinxcontrib-seqdiag\nSphinx extensions with sphinxcontrib-mermaid in the best-practice\nexample configuration files.\n\n- Replace sphinxcontrib-blockdiag with sphinxcontrib-mermaid in conf.py\n- Replace blockdiag/seqdiag with mermaid in requirements-docs.txt\n- Remove Pillow dependency (no longer needed without blockdiag)\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nChange-Id: I928fdbc98e3806ce009454cb8b7509f3001f85c4\nSigned-off-by: Matthew Watkins <mwatkins@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
